# GLOBBLER'S JOURNEY — Bug Fix & Polish Build

## YOU ARE FIXING BUGS IN AN EXISTING GODOT 4.x PROJECT (GDScript)

This is a complete game with 5 chapters. All content exists. You are NOT building new content — you are fixing bugs, broken logic, and missing features identified in a code review.

**For what to fix next, see TASKS.md — that is the source of truth.**

---

## RULES

- Do NOT create new scenes, levels, enemies, or puzzles. Everything already exists.
- Do NOT refactor or reorganize code unless the task specifically says to.
- Do NOT add features beyond what the task describes.
- Fix the exact bug described. Test your fix makes sense by reading surrounding code.
- Keep changes minimal and surgical. Touch only the files mentioned in the task.
- GDScript only. Sarcastic comments in Globbler's voice where appropriate.
- After fixing, update TASKS.md and commit.

